p: In District Court 1st Judicial District Washington Territory

This cause coming up before the Judge of said Court for hearing and the parties having the same upon the pleadings and proofs and the same having been taken under advisement by the Judge, now on this 2nd day of September AD 1873 the said parties by their respective counsel and in persona appeared before said Judge at the Courthouse in Walla Walla W.T.
